result.name: Lake Silver

reviews.text:
This place has a nice view and is a great place to stay in. However, the quality of the clubhouse service is unacceptable and the staff here is unwilling to help. The staff here is way below my expectations. They are hesitant and reluctant to work.

The clubhouse does not allow trolleys into the clubhouse area as it will 'endanger' the lives of children when pushing carts. Staff here likes to play mobile phone games in the front desk and also loves to shop clothes  and accessories using the clubhouse's computer as a motivation to work.

Facilities in Lake Silver is well maintained, however the dishonesty, lack of proper service training and misconduct of the clubhouse staff dragged down the reputation of this beautiful place.
Excellent scene, convenient,  MTR Wu KAI Sha station, near sea
